HEADWORD: Amsonia
<hw>Amsonia</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fr>1</fr> <def>a genus of
herbs and subshrubs with milky juice and showy bluish flowers; native
from Europe to Asia Minor to Japan and North America.</def>⟦br⟧
